1
00:00:40,582 --> 00:00:42,743
快啊，葛斯，快一点
Come on, Gus-Gus. Faster!

2
00:00:42,834 --> 00:00:45,997
杰克，赶什么嘛，赶什么嘛
What's the hurry, Jaq-Jaq?
What's the hurry?

3
00:00:46,088 --> 00:00:47,498
神仙教母来了
Fairy Godmother's here.

4
00:00:47,589 --> 00:00:50,046
她要念仙度瑞拉的故事耶
She's gonna read us
the Cinderelly story.

5
00:00:51,385 --> 00:00:52,591
庞庞
Pom-Pom.

6
00:00:57,557 --> 00:01:01,550
“庞庞”
Pom-Pom

7
00:01:22,624 --> 00:01:24,455
葛斯，来吧
Come on, Gus!

8
00:01:26,295 --> 00:01:31,540
仙度瑞拉跟王子
从此就过着幸福快乐的日子
"Cinderella and the Prince
lived happily ever after.

9
00:01:32,676 --> 00:01:35,088
