Is that your kitty?

486
00:39:12,809 --> 00:39:14,845
真的很可爱
Isn't she precious?

487
00:39:20,316 --> 00:39:22,398
准备跳下一支舞了吗
Ready for the next dance?

488
00:39:50,597 --> 00:39:51,757
乖乖猫
Nice kitty.

489
00:40:06,988 --> 00:40:09,024
我讨厌大象
I hate elephants!

490
00:40:09,907 --> 00:40:13,900
停下来
Stop!

491
00:40:16,581 --> 00:40:20,415
这全是我的错
我真希望神仙教母在这里
This is all my fault!
Wish Fairy Godmother was here.

492
00:40:23,379 --> 00:40:26,041
杰克，这是你可以帮忙的机会了
Jaq, this is your chance to help.

493
00:40:26,132 --> 00:40:27,713
我能做什么
What can I do?

494
00:40:28,468 --> 00:40:32,586
哦！一只大象
