An elephant.
What do you think could stop him?

495
00:40:33,181 --> 00:40:35,547
我命令你停下来
我不知道
-Stop in the name of the King!
-Don't know.

496
00:40:35,642 --> 00:40:38,179
比方说一只老鼠
Perhaps a mouse?

497
00:40:39,812 --> 00:40:42,895
