I'm a mouse! Jaq is back!
I'm a mouse! A mouse!

515
00:41:50,758 --> 00:41:53,500
我是只小老鼠
我是只老鼠，我是只老鼠
M-O-U-S-E. I'm a mousie mousie!

516
00:41:53,594 --> 00:41:57,178
是休爵士的小猫咪
Sir Hugh's kitty!

517
