Aren't you just the sweetest,
little, most precious baby?

519
00:42:10,069 --> 00:42:12,811
杰克，你刚刚好勇敢
Jaq, that was so brave!

520
00:42:12,905 --> 00:42:15,396
玛丽，我真的好想你
Mary, I really missed you.

521
00:42:15,491 --> 00:42:17,482
