是啊
-Thank goodness that's over.
-Yeah.

528
00:43:00,203 --> 00:43:03,070
杰克再也不需要魔法
No more magic for Jaq-Jaq!

529
00:43:03,164 --> 00:43:05,530
一点点也不要吗
哇
-Not even a little?
-Whoa!

530
