I think we've had quite enough magic.

537
00:44:02,974 --> 00:44:04,885
真是一团糟
-What a mess!
-It's a mess, all right.

538
00:44:04,976 --> 00:44:06,136
就是嘛，乱七八糟
非常乱七八糟
A big, stinky mess.

539
00:44:06,227 --> 00:44:08,343
对啊
我们碰过更糟的
-We've seen worse!
-Yeah.

540
00:44:08,437 --> 00:44:10,519
记得安泰西亚恋爱的时候吗
Remember when Anastasia fell in love?

541
