Cinderella's ball is tomorrow night,
so pay attention!

555
00:45:20,384 --> 00:45:23,342
国内所有的单身贵族都会到场
Every noble bachelor
in the kingdom will be there.

556
00:45:23,429 --> 00:45:28,640
如果你们想找到丈夫
你们就必须好好的利用这个好机会
lf you want to find a husband, you have
to mak e the most of this opportunity.

557
00:45:28,726 --> 00:45:31,934
你们不准再让我失望，懂吗
I won't let you fail me, again.

558
00:45:32,772 --> 00:45:34,728
是的，妈妈
-Yes, Mother.
-Yes, Mother.

559
00:45:34,815 --> 00:45:37,352
崔西里亚，脸上再扑点粉
Drizella, pin back those curls.

560
00:45:37,443 --> 00:45:41,061
安泰西亚，腮红再加深一点
Anastasia, put more colour
in your cheeks!

561
00:45:41,155 --> 00:45:45,899
完美的外表
是吸引合格绅士唯一的办法
A perfect appearance is the only way
to attract a proper gentleman.

562
00:45:45,993 --> 00:45:49,861
我一定要替你们找到有钱
