-Maybe a count.
-Or a duke.

564
00:45:52,833 --> 00:45:54,744
一点也没错，过来吧
Precisely.

565
00:45:54,835 --> 00:45:57,793
我们一起去添几件新衣服
Come along now.
We need new gowns for the both of you.

566
00:45:58,339 --> 00:46:01,422
