I'm going to the market in disguise
so no one will recognise me.

571
00:46:28,035 --> 00:46:31,448
顺便还要买个花环
给王子一个惊喜
I want to surprise the Prince
with a garland of flowers.

572
00:46:31,539 --> 00:46:34,656
好耶…
一起来吧
-Want to come along?
-Oh, yeah. Let's go!

573
00:46:34,750 --> 00:46:36,240
葛斯也要去
Gus-Gus come along.

574
00:47:01,193 --> 00:47:02,979
记得这个传统
Remember the tradition.

575
00:47:04,113 --> 00:47:08,106
在舞会上送花环给对方
你们就会长相厮守
Give these to each other at the ball,
and you'll always be together.

576
00:47:09,702 --> 00:47:12,444
你要不要买个玫瑰花环
