Don't you need
a garland of roses for the ball?

577
00:47:16,292 --> 00:47:18,453
保证你可以赢得他的心
Guaranteed to win you his heart.

578
00:47:18,544 --> 00:47:20,956
安泰西亚，你在做什么
Anastasia, what are you doing?

579
00:47:21,047 --> 00:47:23,709
没什么，我来了
Nothing. Coming.

580
00:48:01,921 --> 00:48:05,334
你烤的这些面包闻起来好香哦
Everything smells so good.

581
00:48:05,424 --> 00:48:08,882
小心，还很烫
你想吃一个吗
Would you like one?
Be carefuI. They're hot.

582
00:48:10,596 --> 00:48:13,679
安泰西亚，我们可以走了
Anastasia, I think not.

583
00:48:13,766 --> 00:48:18,226
这店里所有的东西都很廉价
Everything in this shop is inferior.

584
00:48:19,563 --> 00:48:21,770
去盖房子了
你可以用这些硬面包
You can build a house
out of these bricks.

585
00:48:21,857 --> 00:48:23,893
安泰西亚，快来
Come along, Anastasia.

586
00:48:27,655 --> 00:48:32,024
一个卖面包的师傅
你跟他说什么
You're not to say a word
to that shopk eeper.

587
00:48:32,118 --> 00:48:34,905
我绝对不答应
是的，妈妈
-I forbid it!
-Yes, Mother.

588
00:48:37,206 --> 00:48:38,537
看他的表情
He's got that look,

589
00:48:40,000 --> 00:48:42,036
我看过那种神情
and I know that look.

590
00:48:42,128 --> 00:48:43,117
晕船了
Seasick?

591
00:48:45,548 --> 00:48:49,416
这不好笑 我想他们恋爱了
Oh, very funny. I think they're in love.

592
00:48:49,510 --> 00:48:53,219
安泰西亚恋爱
怎么可能，仙度瑞拉
Anastasia's in love?
That's crazy, Cinderelly!

593
00:48:53,305 --> 00:48:56,638
拜托，你们两个
任何人都会恋爱
Come on, you two.
Anyone can fall in love.

594
00:48:56,976 --> 00:48:59,308
安泰西亚例外
Anyone but Anastasia.

595
00:48:59,979 --> 00:49:04,143
也许她需要小小的帮忙
对，很大的帮忙
-Maybe she just needs some help.
-Yeah, lots of help.

596
00:49:04,233 --> 00:49:07,316
当初你们也帮了我很多的忙
记得吗
Well, I had lots of help, too, remember?

597
00:49:08,737 --> 00:49:12,400
我们必须想办法
让他们再碰一次面
We have to figure out
how to get them together again.

598
00:49:12,491 --> 00:49:17,827
对了，把他们引到广场
我们就这么做，
I know! We'll lure them into the square,
and here's how we'll do it.

599
00:49:17,913 --> 00:49:19,244
小鸟去抢她的帽子
The birds will get her hat.

600
00:49:19,331 --> 00:49:21,743
你们去引面包师注意
带安泰西亚回来
Get the baker's attention.
Bring Anastasia here.

601
00:49:21,834 --> 00:49:24,917
他们会在店门口碰面
