What are you doing here
dressed like that?

612
00:51:25,791 --> 00:51:28,157
你看起来像个洗衣女工
You look like a laundry maid.

613
00:51:28,919 --> 00:51:31,501
脸上有蛋的人可不是我
I'm not the one with egg on my face.

614
00:51:36,427 --> 00:51:38,713
我看到你在面包店的事了
I saw you in the baker's shop.

615
00:51:39,638 --> 00:51:41,128
