come back to the castle?

623
00:52:06,790 --> 00:52:09,406
先把你洗干净
然后让你们两个再见一次面
We'll clean you up
and then we'll get you two together.

624
00:52:10,210 --> 00:52:14,078
但是妈妈禁止这样
她认为他配不上我
But Mother forbids it!
She thinks he's beneath me.

625
00:52:14,173 --> 00:52:17,586
可是我认为她错了
那个面包师很棒
And I think she's wrong.
The baker's terrific.

626
00:52:17,676 --> 00:52:19,337
