Trim up the toes

645
00:54:49,953 --> 00:54:51,944
换上洋装和新鞋
Give me the dress and the shoes

646
00:54:52,039 --> 00:54:55,623
戴钻戒和发夹
And the jewellery and clothes

647
00:54:55,709 --> 00:54:58,621
人不可貌相，海水不可斗量
You can judge your books
from how the cover looks

648
00:54:58,712 --> 00:55:02,079
看我锐不可档
Wear makeup by the ounce

649
